reviews.review_text: Nice Show here... I enjoy a crisp charlie SB any day, any time ,any place. NOTE: Tuning is not 13min its actually Terripin and from there the song list is one off. That being the only thing wrong here, it is fantastic and a new part of my collection.
Great show i like this encore
